【Mother’s Day Special 🎉Steamboat Set $98+💥@cocasingapore 】
Mother’s day is around the corner for this extended “Circuit Breaker” period!
Reward & pamper your MAMA this yummy Mother’s Day Special Set steamboat $98+💥(Serves 5-6 Pax) @cocasingapore without leaving your comfort safe home zone!
🤩Featuring a selection of two COCA Signature Broth ( Hua Diao Chicken & Tom Yum) , together with pre-fixed hotpot ingredients such as Thinly Sliced Pork Collar, Wantans , White cabbage , Signature green noodle and many more.
Further complemented with COCA’s comfort dishes such as
◾️💋Mala Xiang Guo
◾️💋Deep Fried Garlic Chicken Winglets (8 pcs)
◾️Garlic Fried Rice (2 servings)
to satisfy your tummies!
📣Mother's Day Special Set available until 💫17 May 2020.
👄Order here: bit.ly/cocaorder
Click link in bio!
Quickly action now & order this value for💰 money steamboat @cocasingapore without trouble your MAMA & enjoy with her at your own comfort save home zone 😉!
“ Happy Mother’s Day” 母亲节快乐🎉！
